  <!-- EN: An already installed set of metal claws, further enhancing the user's close-combat capabilities. -->
  <Wolfein_MetalClawInstalled.description>一副已經安裝好的金屬指爪，使用者的近身搏鬥能力將得到進一步提升。</Wolfein_MetalClawInstalled.description>
